This software generates ensembles of volcanic forcing based on eruption timing and strength. It was developed for creating perturbed volcanic forcing experiments for ModE-Sim and ModE-RA.

**Type:** Research software  
**Release:** Zenodo, 2023  
**Code archive:** [Zenodo record](https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7669569)  
**Source code:** [GitHub repository](https://github.com/shamakson/ModE-Sim-RA_volc_forcing/tree/1.0)
